## Development Setup

- Install dependencies
- Clone the repository
- `pip install -e .`

## Dependencies

- [pythreejs](https://github.com/jovyan/pythreejs/) >= 1.0.0

### Optional
- [openmesh-python](https://graphics.rwth-aachen.de:9000/adielen/openmesh-python) latest



